  <brief_title>Clinical Benefits of a Novel Sleep-focused Mind-body Program on Gulf War Illness (GWI) Symptoms</brief_title>
  <official_title>Investigating Clinical Benefits of a Novel Sleep-focused Mind-body Program on Gulf War Illness (GWI) Symptoms: An Exploratory Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
